    "summary": "The user asks about taking ibuprofen while on the anticoagulant warfarin and then requests a dosage for acetaminophen as a safer alternative. The assistant correctly identifies the risk of combining NSAIDs with warfarin and provides standard, safe dosage information and caveats for acetaminophen.",
